'''HelloFresh SE'''是一家总部位于[[德国|德国]][[柏林|柏林]]的国际[[快煮餐|快煮餐]]公司。它是美国最大的快煮餐提供商<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|url=https://www.recode.net/2018/3/26/17165030/hellofresh-blue-apron-meal-kit-delivery-marketshare-acquisition-organic-green-chef|title=HelloFresh is now bigger than Blue Apron in the U.S.|work=Recode|first=Rani|author=Molla|date=2018-03-26|accessdate=2018-08-08|archive-date=2018-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808203207/https://www.recode.net/2018/3/26/17165030/hellofresh-blue-apron-meal-kit-delivery-marketshare-acquisition-organic-green-chef|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并且在加拿大，西欧（包括卢森堡，德国，比利时，法国和荷兰），新西兰和澳大利亚都有业务。2017年11月[[首次公开募股|IPO]]后，该公司已在[[法兰克福证券交易所|法兰克福证券交易所]]上市。

== 历史 ==
HelloFresh由多米尼克·里希特（{{lang|en|Dominik Richter}}）、托马斯·格里塞尔（{{lang|en|Thomas Griesel}}）和杰西卡·尼尔森（{{lang|en|Jessica Nilsson}}）于2011年11月在德国柏林成立。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://tech.eu/features/2356/hellofresh-funding-profile/|title=Why Berlin meal delivery startup HelloFresh just raised $50m|date=2014-08-07|work=Tech.eu|accessdate=2018-02-07|first=Charmaine|author=Li|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926130929/http://tech.eu/features/2356/hellofresh-funding-profile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年初，他们向付费客户提供打包快煮餐。前10个客户的快煮餐是由里希特和格里塞尔打包并手动交付的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Our story|url=https://www.hellofreshgroup.com/websites/hellofresh/English/140/our-story.html|accessdate=2018-03-13|work=HelloFresh Group|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427095254/https://www.hellofreshgroup.com/websites/hellofresh/English/140/our-story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>HelloFresh是较早进入快煮餐行业中公司之一。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/06/18/hellofresh-a-meal-delivery-start-up-raises-50-million/|date=2014-06-18|title=HelloFresh, a Meal Delivery Start-Up, Raises $50 Million|author=de la Merced|first=Michael J.|work=DealBook|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926131151/https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/06/18/hellofresh-a-meal-delivery-start-up-raises-50-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最初，他们受德国创业工作室公司[[火箭网|火箭网]]资助，于2012年将业务扩展到[[荷兰|荷兰]]、英国、美国和[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]。到2014年，据该公司数据显示，他们每月提供100万份餐点。他们先后在2012年和2013年的融资中分别筹集到1000万美元和700万美元，在2014年的融资中筹集了5000万美元。 

截至2015年3月，该公司已拥有25万用户，但仍未实现盈利。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=https://www.ft.com/content/658e86be-5d23-11e5-97e9-7f0bf5e7177b|title=Funding round values German grocery start-up HelloFresh at €2.6bn|date=2015-09-17|work=Financial Times|language=en-GB|accessdate=2018-02-07|archive-date=2018-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611051856/https://www.ft.com/content/658e86be-5d23-11e5-97e9-7f0bf5e7177b|dead-url=no}}</ref>是年9月，在融资过程中，它的估值达到了26亿欧元，筹集了7500万欧元，成为了一家[[独角兽企业|独角兽企业]]。当时该公司的多数股权仍归火箭网所有。出于投资者对公司拟定价值的担忧，该公司在11月取消了IPO计划。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/hellofresh-ipo/meal-delivery-firm-hellofresh-puts-ipo-on-hold-idUSL8N1330QC20151108|title=Meal delivery firm HelloFresh puts IPO on hold|author=Huebner|first=Alexander|first2=Ludwig|author2=Burger|date=2015-11-08|work=Reuters|accessdate=2018-02-07|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801212256/https://www.reuters.com/article/hellofresh-ipo/meal-delivery-firm-hellofresh-puts-ipo-on-hold-idUSL8N1330QC20151108|dead-url=no}}</ref>该网站在年内取得大幅发展，截至10月底已有53万用户。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/r-loss-making-online-meal-delivery-firm-hellofresh-plans-flotation-2015-10|title=Loss-making online meal delivery firm HelloFresh plans to go public|work=Business Insider|accessdate=2018-02-07|first=Arno|author=Schuetze|first2=Alexander|author2=Hübner|date=2015-10-28|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318115916/http://www.businessinsider.com/r-loss-making-online-meal-delivery-firm-hellofresh-plans-flotation-2015-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2016年7月已拥有75万用户，2017年第三季度为130万。<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|first=Richard|author=Vines|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-20/is-hellofresh-good-a-top-chef-tests-alongside-marley-spoon-goose-box-farmison-co|title=A Michelin-Star Chef Tests Four Home-Cooking Delivery Services|date=2016-07-20|work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823190823/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-20/is-hellofresh-good-a-top-chef-tests-alongside-marley-spoon-goose-box-farmison-co|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/10/business/dealbook/hellofresh-ipo.html|title=HelloFresh, the Meal Delivery Service, Pursues I.P.O. in Frankfurt|author=Bray|first=Chad|date=2017-10-10|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012061018/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/10/business/dealbook/hellofresh-ipo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年12月，哈罗生鲜公司在最新的G轮融资中获得 Baillie Gifford 独家8500万欧元投资。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mg21.com/hlfff.html|title=德国半成品净菜电子商务市场：哈罗生鲜HelloFresh SE(HLFFF)|publisher=美股之家|date=2021-09-17|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921011929/https://www.mg21.com/hlfff.html}}</ref>

2017年10月，该公司宣布计划在法兰克福证券交易所进行[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]，筹集到3.5亿美元。<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/10/business/dealbook/hellofresh-ipo.html|title=HelloFresh, the Meal Delivery Service, Pursues I.P.O. in Frankfurt|author=Bray|first=Chad|date=2017-10-10|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012061018/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/10/business/dealbook/hellofresh-ipo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月2日，该公司完成了IPO，市值达到17亿欧元。<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=http://fortune.com/2017/11/02/blue-apron-hellofresh-ipo/|title=HelloFresh Is Worth Much More to Investors Than Blue Apron|work=Fortune|agency=Reuters|date=2017-11-02|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111105130/http://fortune.com/2017/11/02/blue-apron-hellofresh-ipo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在首次公开募股时，该公司的市值是其在美国最大的竞争对手[[Blue_Apron|Blue Apron]]的两倍多。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/hellofresh-ipo/update-1-hellofresh-makes-positive-debut-valuation-double-rival-blue-apron-idUSL8N1N82AT|title=UPDATE 2-HelloFresh's bright start contrasts with Blue Apron struggles|date=2017-11-02|work=Reuters|accessdate=2018-03-07|first=Eric|author=Auchard|first2=Arno|author2=Schuetze|archive-date=2018-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180101130802/https://www.reuters.com/article/hellofresh-ipo/update-1-hellofresh-makes-positive-debut-valuation-double-rival-blue-apron-idUSL8N1N82AT|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2018年3月，HelloFresh收购了美国快煮餐公司Green Chef<ref name=":6"/>。2018年10月，总部位于加拿大[[多伦多|多伦多]]的HelloFresh分公司收购了加拿大餐厨公司Chefs Plate。<ref>{{Cite web|title=HelloFresh eyes bigger slice of Canadian meal kit market|url=https://www.supermarketnews.com/online-retail/hellofresh-eyes-bigger-slice-canadian-meal-kit-market|accessdate=2018-12-13|author=Redman|date=2018-11-28|first=Russell|work=supermarketnews.com|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031411/https://www.supermarketnews.com/online-retail/hellofresh-eyes-bigger-slice-canadian-meal-kit-market|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2019年，火箭网通过{{Le|簿记建档|Book building}}向国际机构投资者出售了HelloFresh剩余的股份。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.retaildetail.eu/en/news/general/rocket-internet-sees-profits-almost-double|title=Rocket Internet sees profits almost double|date=2019-09-19|accessdate=2020-08-12|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801135401/https://www.retaildetail.eu/en/news/general/rocket-internet-sees-profits-almost-double|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/dgap-news-rocket-internet-se-rocket-internet-intends-to-place-its-entire-shareholding-in-hellofresh-se-1028195650|title=DGAP-News: Rocket Internet SE: Rocket Internet intends to place its entire shareholding in HelloFresh SE|author=EQS Group|date=2019-05-13|accessdate=2020-08-12|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801171650/https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/dgap-news-rocket-internet-se-rocket-internet-intends-to-place-its-entire-shareholding-in-hellofresh-se-1028195650|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2018年底，火箭网占据了HelloFresh30.6%的股份。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Interim Condensed Consolidated Financial Statements for the Period January 1 to June 30, 2019|url=https://www.rocket-internet.com/sites/default/files/investors/2019_HY1_RISE_Interim%20FS_EN.pdf|date=2019-09-19|quote=The decrease of investments in associates by EUR 232.8 million primarily originates from the disposal of shares in HelloFresh and Westwing}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

== 商业模式 ==
HelloFresh的商业模式是准备一顿饭所需的食材，并将其交付给客户，然后客户必须使用食谱卡<ref>{{Cite web|title=What's in the box?|url=http://support.hellofresh.ca/hc/en-us/articles/360011780314-What-s-in-the-box-|accessdate=2019-01-08|work=HelloFresh Canada|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109111007/https://support.hellofresh.ca/hc/en-us/articles/360011780314-What-s-in-the-box-|dead-url=no}}</ref>烹制这顿饭，大约需要30-40分钟。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.top10mealdeliveryservices.com/reviews/hellofresh-uk-review/|title=HelloFresh UK Review|date=2017-08-31|work=Top 10 Meal Delivery Services|accessdate=2018-03-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417192058/https://www.top10mealdeliveryservices.com/reviews/hellofresh-uk-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>通常其每周提供的餐点为约三顿两人份，费用约为60至70美元。<ref name=":1"/>顾客可在19种食谱中选择。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How It Works|url=https://www.hellofresh.com/how-it-works/|accessdate=2018-03-13|work=HelloFresh|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212160715/https://www.hellofresh.com/how-it-works/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在美国，HelloFresh仿照竞争对手Blue Apron提供葡萄酒订阅服务。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Elin|author=McCoy|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-03/wine-on-demand-rating-bottles-from-blue-apron-hello-fresh-caviar|title=Wine on Demand? Rating Bottles From Blue Apron, Hello Fresh, Caviar|date=2017-11-03|work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]]|accessdate=2018-03-13|language=en|archive-date=2018-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418083452/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-03/wine-on-demand-rating-bottles-from-blue-apron-hello-fresh-caviar|dead-url=no}}</ref>在一些市场中，它可提供仅需20分钟就完成的“快速盒”餐（{{Lang|en|Rapid Box}}）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/spiralisers-sushi-mats-ice-cream-11866020|title=Average UK household boasts staggering £415 worth of unused cooking gadgets|author=Rudd|first=Andy|date=2018-01-17|work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]]|accessdate=2018-03-13|archive-date=2018-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417192139/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/spiralisers-sushi-mats-ice-cream-11866020|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

截至2017年11月，该公司在美国的业务占公司收入的60％。<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=http://fortune.com/2017/11/02/blue-apron-hellofresh-ipo/|title=HelloFresh Is Worth Much More to Investors Than Blue Apron|work=Fortune|agency=Reuters|date=2017-11-02|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111105130/http://fortune.com/2017/11/02/blue-apron-hellofresh-ipo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>至2018年2月，在美国市场的份额占到33%<ref name=":6"/>。HelloFresh还在[[英国|英国]]、[[德国|德国]]、[[奥地利|奥地利]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]、[[比利时|比利时]]、[[卢森堡|卢森堡]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[法国|法国]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[丹麦|丹麦]]提供服务。

== 批评 ==
HelloFresh被批评称运送的饭菜过分包装导致浪费。<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|first=Richard|author=Vines|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-20/is-hellofresh-good-a-top-chef-tests-alongside-marley-spoon-goose-box-farmison-co|title=A Michelin-Star Chef Tests Four Home-Cooking Delivery Services|date=2016-07-20|work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823190823/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-20/is-hellofresh-good-a-top-chef-tests-alongside-marley-spoon-goose-box-farmison-co|dead-url=no}}</ref>该公司还因其营销成本一直高昂但无法盈利而受到批评。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/rocket-internets-marketing-costs-keep-profit-at-bay-1474551037|title=HelloFresh, a German Tech Incubator's Star, Still Struggles to Deliver|author=Woo|first=Stu|date=2016-09-22|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en-US|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2018-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180119180400/https://www.wsj.com/articles/rocket-internets-marketing-costs-keep-profit-at-bay-1474551037|dead-url=no}}</ref>公司的{{Le|顾客保留|Customer retention}}率低，根据一项独立分析，第一周后不到50％的客户放弃使用该公司的服务，而六个月后只剩下仍不到10％的客户。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Sarah|author=Kessler|url=https://www.fastcompany.com/3064792/meal-kit-customers-dine-and-dash|title=Meal-Kit Customers Dine And Dash|date=2016-10-20|work=Fast Company|accessdate=2018-02-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110050627/https://www.fastcompany.com/3064792/meal-kit-customers-dine-and-dash|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

